878
01:05:36,708 --> 01:05:37,541
Moremi.

879
01:05:40,291 --> 01:05:43,125
El rojo es mi color favorito.

880
01:05:53,500 --> 01:05:56,875
A pesar de haberle dicho
a la señorita Oluwa...

881
01:05:58,583 --> 01:06:01,833
